Program: Outlook
Title: Altered Photos in Newspapers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbqyt
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at the altering of newspaper photographs with a visit to the pictures department of The Guardian and a discussion with Eamonn McCabe, Horst Faas and Stuart Locklear. Also, homelessness in Nigeria, hymn singing in Malawi and Willard Wigan who makes minasclue sculptures only visible under microscope. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less